<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-2340] Generated server implementation does not send response type EXCEPTION on the Thrift.TApplicationExceptionType.UNKNOWN_METHOD exception</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2340</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When Node.js server implementation gets an Thrift.TApplicationExceptionType.UNKNOWN_METHOD error it sends back a response with type = 0 and not type = 3, which is Thrift.MessageType.EXCEPTION.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It makes Node.js servers incompatible with Thrift Finagle clients.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
